1324547752.text: "Interestingly, using a tamoxifen inducible, Cre mediated FAK deletion model to inactivate FAK from endothelium of blood vessels in adult mice, it was noted that the loss of FAK function is not lethal due to the functional compensation of Pyk2 (FAK related protein proline rich tyrosine kinase 2) in which endothelial cells in blood vessels in adult mice, it was noted that the loss of FAK function or cultured endothelial cells have the adaptive capacity of switching to Pyk2 dependent signaling to maintain the lost FAK function."

mentions.text: Cre mediated FAK deletion model to inactivate FAK
